# rel/vm.args.eex — VM arguments for auth2api_ex release
#
# Evaluated at release build time; variables like <%= @release.name %> are available.
# Runs under systemd / Docker without a TTY → -noshell required for OTP 28+.

-noshell
-noinput

## Increase number of concurrent ports/sockets
+Q 65536

## Tweak GC to run more often (optional)
##-env ERL_FULLSWEEP_AFTER 10

## Enable deployment without epmd
## (requires changing both vm.args and remote.vm.args)
##-start_epmd false -erl_epmd_port 6789